trans-unit.source: Provides a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.PropertyTab"></xref> that can display events for selection and linking.

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IServiceProvider>使用。</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the specified object can be extended.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出是否可以擴充指定的物件。

trans-unit.source: The object to test for extensibility.
trans-unit.target: 若要測試擴充性物件。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified object can be extended; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the default property from the specified object.
trans-unit.target: 從指定的物件取得預設屬性。

trans-unit.target: 要擷取的預設屬性的物件。

trans-unit.source: Gets all the properties of the event tab that match the specified attributes.
trans-unit.target: 取得所有事件 索引標籤符合的屬性指定的屬性。

trans-unit.source: The event tab properties are determined from the event properties returned from a component's event service.
trans-unit.target: 事件 索引標籤的內容由從元件的事件服務傳回的事件屬性。

trans-unit.source: The component to retrieve the properties of.
trans-unit.target: 要擷取的屬性的元件。

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Attribute> that indicates the attributes of the event properties to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: 陣列<xref:System.Attribute>，表示要擷取的事件屬性的屬性。</xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptorCollection"></xref> that contains the properties.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptorCollection"> </xref>其中包含的屬性。

trans-unit.source: This will be an empty <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptorCollection"></xref> if the component does not implement an event service.
trans-unit.target: 這會是空白<xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptorCollection"></xref>如果元件未實作事件服務。

trans-unit.target: 取得所有屬性的 [事件] 索引標籤，符合指定的屬性和內容。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain context information.

trans-unit.source: This will be an empty <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptorCollection"></xref> if the component does not implement an event service.
